            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1527441445,
            "creation_date": 1527407990,
            "body": "<p>If you don\u2019t need to know the line or column in the \u201cdo something\u201d code (not stated in question), you could:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Arrays.stream(Myarray).flatMap(Arrays:stream)\n    .forEach(n -&gt; /* do something with \u201cn\u201d, the cell value */);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
